contentfulGallery.title: A Serene Moment: The Pristine White Rabbit
contentfulGallery.author: DALL·E

childMarkdownRemark.html: Create an image of a small, fluffy white rabbit with upright ears and dark eyes, sitting on a soft surface with a gentle look. The rabbit should have a round body, short fur, and look pristine and soft to the touch. The background should be simple and unobtrusive, focusing the attention on the rabbit itself.
